Revision history for Perl class Text::CSV::Smart.

1.01  Sat May 30 2026
	- fixed minor typos
	- change default separator to comma
	- make new($filename, \%args) a reader shortcut and allow explicit
	  reader/writer/appender dispatch
	- normalize header field names for safe AUTOLOAD access
	- reject empty, reserved, numeric, and duplicate field names
	- document row helpers and parser defaults
	- add tests for EOF, parser errors, width mismatches, TSV options,
	  and field-name normalization

1.00  Fri Sep 07
	- first release with tests

0.01  Mon Aug 27 13:03:16 2012
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AX Text::CSV::Smart
